<BaseLayout title="Tiered Pools of Tolantongo — 6 Natural Pools at 36°C" description="The tiered pools of Tolantongo: 6 natural limestone pools in cascade with thermal water at 36°C (97°F) and views of the 800 m canyon. Included with general admission." canonical="/en/grottoes/tiered-pools/" schema={schema} lang="en">
